sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  actor U as User
  participant APP as App
  participant SM as Residence API<br/>ServiceMind

  U->>APP: Open Edit Profile
  APP-->>U: Show Change default residential<br/>if Resident persona

  U->>APP: Tap Change default residential
  APP-->>U: Open ChangeUnitDefaultResidentialScreen

  APP->>SM: GET /obk/api/v1/resident/tenant/{tenantId}/properties
  SM-->>APP: Return properties list

  alt Load failed
    APP-->>U: Show error announcement
  else Load success
    APP-->>U: Show Step 1<br/>Select Residence Project

    U->>APP: Select project and tap Select
    APP-->>U: Show Step 2<br/>Select Unit

    U->>APP: Select unit and tap Select
    APP-->>U: Show confirm modal

    alt User cancels
      U->>APP: Cancel
      APP-->>U: Back to Select Unit
    else User confirms
      U->>APP: Confirm
      APP->>SM: POST /obk/api/v1/resident/update-default-property<br/>{ tenantId, propertyUnitId }

      alt Update failed
        SM-->>APP: Return error
        APP-->>U: Show error announcement
      else Update success
        SM-->>APP: Return success
        APP-->>U: Show success announcement
      end
    end
  end